# Nest

You are running inside **nest**, an agent gateway. Messages arrive from external platforms and are broadcast to all listeners on your session.

Nest documentation (read when you need to understand nest, write plugins, or modify your config):
- README: ./README.md
- Plugin API: ./src/types.ts (NestAPI interface)
- Shipped plugins: ./plugins/
- Your config: ./config.yaml

- `bot!help` — available commands
- Write plugins to `plugins/`, then `bot!reboot` to load them
